# Task 2: Stock Price Prediction

## Objective

The objective of this task is to predict stock closing prices using historical data.

## Dataset

Apple (AAPL) stock data collected using yfinance.

## Model

Linear Regression

## Work Done

* Loaded stock data using yfinance
* Selected features (Open, High, Low, Volume)
* Split data into training and testing sets
* Trained Linear Regression model
* Compared predicted vs actual values

## Results

* Model captured general price trends
* Predictions were close to actual values
* Minor deviations observed

## Tools Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Scikit-learn
* Matplotlib
* yfinance

